Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:01:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where am I?\N--Oh, you shouldn't move yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! The golden belfry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:02:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have the duty to protect it to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush, Wyper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vearth, at least, is not refusing anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... Right now, at least,\Nno one wants to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's party time!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The long battle of 400 years had ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the citizens of Skypiea continued\Ntheir joyous party day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Made It Here! The Yarn the Poneglyphs Spin"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... I can't drink any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is it?\N--Nami, wake everyone up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna steal the gold and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.09,0:03:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:04:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "idiot"?!\NYou're louder than I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm louder, you say?!\NYou're the louder one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're calling me loud\Nwhen you're really super loud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice is the one that's\Nreally super-mega-ultra loud!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's true!!\NI'm talking loud because you're loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shut up! I can't sleep!!\N--You're the one who spoke loud first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! You're the loud one!!\N--It wasn't me! It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a delicate woman! I wouldn't yell\Nwith my mouth wide open, would I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! There's no way\NI'd do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See? See?! Your mouth is wide open!\N--Geez, wake up, sleepyhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you did hit me here! Here! It's really true!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's because you ticked me off!\N--Nami-san! Good morning!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh? It's not morning yet!\N--Yeah, yeah... Go ahead and\Nbe feeble-minded like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Like I said, you don't\Nhave to shout, you know!!\N--What do you mean, "feeble-minded"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Sea people sure like to party, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fourth day in a row.\NTheir vitality isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, guys! It's not often that\Nwe get to visit a sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it so that you'll have no regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! We found the golden bell!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's stuck on the fallen Giant Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pulling it out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can help, come to the\Nwestern seashore! Hurry! Hurry up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, guys! Gather everyone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the western seashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The belfry was found!\N--Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--At the western seashore.\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you sure?!\N--Yeah! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they found\Nthe bell that fell in the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Those who can move,\Ngather at the western seashore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The belfry was found!\NIt's at the western seashore!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The belfry was?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! We still need more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the pride of our ancestors' city,\NShandora. We'll get it at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it everything you got!!\NOne more time!! One, two...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull harder!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubber band?! So you call this a rubber band?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! My Usopp Rubber Band did 90%\Nof the work of taking Giant Jack down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa!\N--Whoa! Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one in the world that has them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa!\N--Whoa! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... put that aside for now.\NI'd like to show you this iron sheet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, ladies and gentlemen!\NThis is no ordinary iron sheet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:08:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tore it off from the Going Merry,\Nour ship that endured very hard travels
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the Grand Line, as well as Eneru's\Nattacks! It's the "King of Iron Sheets"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?! You guys want iron, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you trade me dials for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I want this rubber band!\NI'll trade you for this rubber band!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I want one, too! Is that okay?!\N--Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa... Are they serious?!\N--Give me one, too!\N--Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water, light, fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things whose shape is transient...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things with no form...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cut them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shells! I got shells! Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Lucky, lucky! I got so lucky!\N--You're in a good mood, aren't you, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the negotiation go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear that? I got lots of dials!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I press it and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for me! With this many dials,\NI can do many different things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Usopp factory'll be running full steam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro, if you make\Nyour swords Flavor Swords
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and store the smell of\Nstuff like melons in them,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can enjoy your everyday training!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No thanks.\N--Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I can make\NNami's Clima Takt stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My slingshot will be incredible, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where are Robin, Luffy and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others are still inside.\NRobin went somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case... this snake's really conked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept dancing day after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...though I don't know\Nwhat he was so happy about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, they'd better come out soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because if he wakes up,\Nhe could give them a hard time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This good-tempered snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! You just don't know\Nhow troublesome he can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This good-tempered snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, you can be so\Noptimistic because you didn't see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what a pain this snake can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This good-tempered snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now listen here, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This good-tempered snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It was a Tone Dial!\N--Don't do stupid stuff like that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's stupid! It's really stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! What does this snake eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we there, yet, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! There they are!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:11:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty! It looks just like the ones\Nthat we saw at the monkeys' house!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? See? See?! There's all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it awesome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How beautiful...\N--Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I didn't expect it to be this...\N--How magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one of the side columns has been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but there isn't much we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is... the Poneglyph...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stone that our ancestors\Nrisked the city's life to protect...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is written on it, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something we're better off not knowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hold our true motive in your\Nhearts and speak not of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the ones who weave history...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the sounding of the grand belfry..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know those words?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were carved on the Shandoran ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were the keepers,\Nentrusted with this for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... You can read those characters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poseidon, the "ancient weapon"\Nnamed after a God...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its whereabouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! What's that?!\N--She said "ancient"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ancient weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it talking about something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...separate from Pluton\Nthat I read about in Alabasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that one shot from Pluton\Nwill completely destroy an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that there are such dangerous\Nthings in this world waiting to be found...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, this was a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Aren't those the same kind of\Ncharacters on that engraving next to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gol D. Roger"...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it here. I will guide this\Ntext to the ends of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Gol D. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of the Pirates...! Could this mean\Nthat he came to this sky island, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth do these words mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, more importantly,\Nwhy can he use these characters?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it says Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Blue Sea pirate who came\Nto this sky more than 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So his name is engraved there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I don't know how he reached this bell,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this sure is indelible proof that he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, there're two\Nkinds of Poneglyph stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ones with information, and others\Nthat indicate their whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this stone is one of\Nthe ones with information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I made it here. I will guide this\Ntext to the ends of the earth."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guide this text... Guide...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...!\NCould the Rio Poneglyph be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief... This Poneglyph\Nhas already fulfilled its role!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I bet those Poneglyphs with\Ninformation scattered around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will, when put together, become one text
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that will fill the "Blank History"\Nfor the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the text\Ncompleted by connecting them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Rio Poneglyph,\Nwhich still does not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gol D. Roger, King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely delivered this text to its destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Then...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...does that mean that our duty\Nhas been fulfilled as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... don't have to... fight any longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:17:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Our ancestors' wish\Nhas been fulfilled, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chief!\N--Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good... Good... So our duty has been fulfilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have to guide the text on those\NPoneglyphs that I read in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the end of the Grand Line... to Raftel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, the feeling that straw hat kid\Ngives me is reminiscent of Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Monkey D. Luffy.\NMy interest in him never fades.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D? I see. He's got the same letter in his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... and I'm sure it's a big issue\Nthat has something to do with history.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:18:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, young lady...\NYou guys wanted gold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it's more valuable\Nthan Vearth in the Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about taking the broken belfry column,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though we can't give you the bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, we have to show our\Nappreciation to you guys somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right!\N--Don't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?! They'll be happy to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then! Let's bring\Nthis to the Blue Sea people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrap it with cloths! It's hard to carry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give this to those who saved our land!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this thing's huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Robin doing? She's late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this place is\Nso empty. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did the\Nguerrillas and angels go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's better they aren't here.\NIf they find us, they'll chase us around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're trying to steal this much\Ngold and run, they won't just let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Nami and Conis are preparing\Nto set sail, but we still have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, Sanji, do you\Nhave something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not until we get to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've gotta have\Nsomething to munch on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give me some!\N--What a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We don't have to wait for that woman, do we?\N--I can't give you what I\Ndon't have! Just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go on ahead and get on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Idiot! Don't!\N--Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Idiot Moss Head!\N--Moss Head Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go into the forest alone, you won't\Nmake it three steps without getting lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! It's Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo, Robin!! Hurry! Hurry up!\NWe've gotta run!! We stole some gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Don't say that!\NTake a good look behind her!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all coming back here together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's tons of them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! This is bad! This is super bad!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's that? A huge cannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's gotta be it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all came back all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry to the ship! We can no longer stay here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check this out! We got a good catch!\NThe bag's stuffed! We're rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? They all have bags on their back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... Are they already leaving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop, you guys!! Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Stop! Stop, you guys!\N--See?! They found us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll strike a pose and say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys say, "Stop! Stop!" but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Tell them, Usopp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We risked our lives to come\Nall the way to this sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right!\N--And we've found the legendary city of gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Robin-chan! Hurry up! We'll be caught!\N--How the heck can we, proud pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just go back empty-handed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Caught?! What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we want to do is thank them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Miss, aren't you guys\Ngonna take this gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Run!!\N--Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all after us! It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that?! Wasn't I cool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan! Hurry!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Keep running all the\Nway to the end of the sky!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling lonely, talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gaze at the heavens\Nas you wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the moon,\Nyou keep your gaze constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your deep reflection wanes\Nas you slowly disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are, let those words guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream, you travelers who spend\Ncountless nights drifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you may not be able to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely start moving forward again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, everyone! We'll split the treasure\Nonce we get back down, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep it safe, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where?!\N--It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'll tell you where\NI hide my secret stash, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.56,0:23:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.06,0:23:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie! Her eyes say she's telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, guys! We're going back to the Blue Sea!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Off to the Blue Sea!! Finale Woven by Feelings"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.83,0:23:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
